FOOT & MOUTH DISEASE - NEW ZEALAND: PREVENTIVE MEASURES
*******************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
ProMED-mail is a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
<http://www.isid.org>

Sponsored in part by Elsevier, publisher of
